fcp-desc-freally-capture = A local-first, cross-platform live-streaming & recording studio (OBS-class): a real-time GPU scene compositor, multi-track recording, and multistream to every platform at once — entirely on your machine. No accounts, no telemetry, no cloud.
fcp-desc-freally-vault = A local-first, zero-knowledge, end-to-end-encrypted password, passkey & secrets manager. KeePass-compatible, memory-safe Rust core, completely free — your vault never leaves your machine.
fcp-desc-freally-player = A local-first, cross-platform media player that plays virtually anything with hardware acceleration — a modern UI, a real media library, and streaming, with no ads and no telemetry.
fcp-desc-freally-av = Freally's local-first anti-virus for Windows, macOS, and Linux. On the way — not yet available to download.
fcp-desc-freally-studio = A full-featured DAW with AI pattern generation across 35+ genres, an FL-style mixer, arrangement timeline, and audio-clip editor. Pre-release — not yet available to download.
fcp-desc-freally-sourcerer = This Freally-brand app is on the way. Not yet available to download.
fcp-desc-freally-file-manager = This Freally-brand app is on the way. Not yet available to download.
